; OpVariable minimum = 4 (header + result-type + result-id + storage-class);
; WordCount=3 is malformed.
; Test that malformed input is rejected early rather than silently causing
; integer underflow and potential process hang.

; RUN: not llvm-spirv %s -to-binary -o %t.spv 2>&1 | FileCheck %s
; CHECK: InvalidWordCount:

119734787 65536 0 8 0
2 Capability Kernel
2 Capability Addresses
3 MemoryModel 1 2
4 TypeInt 3 32 0
4 TypePointer 4 7 3
3 Variable 4 5 7
